0x33468EDC08E371F60xCF428FA4// GetDlcVehicleData
BOOL GET_DLC_VEHICLE_DATA(int dlcVehicleIndex, Any* outData);Parameters:dlcVehicleIndex: takes a number from 0 to GET_NUM_DLC_VEHICLES() - 1.outData: a struct of 3 8-byte items.Returns: A boolean value return if find or not the dlcVehicleIndex.The Second item in the struct *(Hash *)(outData + 1) is the vehicle hash.
